data.description: This 3 bdrm, 2 ba split floor plan is ready for new owners! Located in a established, non HOA neighborhood, right off of St John's Heritage Pkwy, this home has new plumbing, new flooring and new AC in 2023! The updated kitchen is equipped with stainless appliances, wood cabinetry, open shelving, and granite countertops.The living and dining combo has cathedral ceilings and dual sliders that lead out to the extra 252 sf enclosed sunroom. The primary bedroom has a full bath with a walk in closet! Waiting for your finishing touches, this home is conveniently located just 10 min from I-95, the Intracoastal, St Johns River, Palm Crossing, West Melbourne, dining,  and Heritage High School. Great investment opportunity!
